    public interface MutableResult<E>
extends Result<E>
    Result from which elements can be added or removed.

    • Method Detail

      • add

        void add(E element)
        Adds the specified element. This element will be returned in any subsequent Result.iterator() but will not be persisted to the backing store until update is called for the entity holding this object.
        Parameters:
        element - to add

      • remove

        void remove(E element)
        Removes the specified element. This element will no longer be returned in any subsequent Result.iterator(). Note the element is not actually removed from the backing store until the entity holding this object is updated.
        Parameters:
        element - to remove
